events.name: ゴブリン討伐　ラスト

parameters:
\n< Serena >...I can't find anything. Is it just my
imagination...?

\n< Serena >Wha... what... a green, baby... is it a goblin
hatchling? This...
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Ag... Agigi...

\n< Serena >U-uhh... w-what...! What is this... just looking
at it... makes my heart flutter...!
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Gee...!
\n< Serena >N-No...!

\n< Serena >Haah... I ended up running away without
thinking...

\n< Serena >Even though it's supposed to be a powerless
infant, just because it has a shape similar to a
human, it feels so grotesque...

\n< Serena >Extermination... is... it okay...? Anyway, it
won't last long with just one.
\n< Serena >Or rather, I don't want to go back to the cabin...

\n< Serena >However, if I don't have any proof of
extermination this time, Master will get angry at
me again...
\n< Serena >No, I did make an effort. Yes.
\n< Serena >No, I did make an effort. Yes.
\n<Guild Master>Yes... Yes, I thought so too...

\n< Serena >Y-Yes. With this, there are only \V[2501] more
left.
'　ゴブリン討伐は完了だ。宿に帰って休もう。'
'クエストをクリアした。'
回想セーブ 温泉街ゴブリン敗北
\n< Serena >Hm, mmm... huh!?
\n< Goblin >Gye! Gyiii!
\n< Serena >Huh!?
\n< Serena >W-What... is this situation...!?

\n< Serena >(I've been taken to their nest...? Being
restrained by goblins... There are roughly seven
of them around me...)

\n< Serena >I have the ring... If only I could create an
Affabel...
\n< Goblin >Gya!
\n< Serena >Stop it! Don't pull me!!
\n< Serena >Stop, stop--
\n< Goblin >Gya!
\n< Serena >Uwaaa!? M-My clothes...!? L-Let go! Don't look!!

\n< Serena >(Y-You... my concentration... is disrupted...! To
be thrown off by something like this... my
equipment's regeneration...!)
\n< Goblin >Giggle giggle...
\n< Serena >Haa, haa...?
\n< Serena >!?... W-What are you rubbing against me?!
\n< Serena >Disgusting...! No...!
\n< Goblin >Gyuhee... Gihh...
\n< Serena >Huh...!?
\n< Serena >Ah...uh...a...!

\n< Serena >What... this isn't an attack... what are they
doing to me... what is the goblin doing...?
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
\n< Goblin >....

\n< Serena >Stop... don't bring that near me... it's something
very disgusting...!

\n< Serena >(It seems like something I shouldn't be looking
at...!)
\n< Serena >Get away! Don't... stop... ah!
\n< Serena >Yaaaaaaaah!?
\n< Serena >No! No! Not there...!
\n< Serena >Push, press...! Huh!? No...!
\n< Goblin >Ghehehe... Ghi!

エリカ HK_PT01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1

\n< Erika >Oorara! You goblins! Making a ruckus in broad
daylight!
\n< Serena >Ah... Erika, my lord...!?
\n< Erika >Oh? Hey, who do I see? It's Serena, isn't it!
\n< Erika >Geez, talk about a close call!

\n< Erika >Fine, I guess I have no choice! I'll consider it a
loan!
\n< Erika >Ahh, these goblins are so slimy...!
\n< Erika >Serena, are you okay?
\n< Serena >I'm fine. I'm sorry, Erika-sama... I'm saved.

\n< Erika >Be careful. Even weaklings have the power to kill
humans.
\n< Serena >It really hit me.

\n< Erika >Alright then, I guess I'll go home... Wait, it's
impossible with that appearance, isn't it?

\n< Erika >I'll go look for some clothes or fabric that you
can wear over it.
\n< Serena >I'm sorry...
\n< Serena >*sigh*...
\n< Serena >What... was that, I wonder...
\n< Serena >I was scared...

\n< Serena >It's a different kind of pain... a different kind
of death...

\n< Serena >It feels like a dream. I don't think I'll be able
to forget it for a while...
\n<Guild Master>It seems like you had quite an experience, Erika.
\n< Serena >Hmm... I have no face to show.

\n<Guild Master>How about it? Aren't you tired of being an
adventurer? It's painful, it's disgusting, and on
top of that, it stinks.
\n< Serena >....
\n< Serena >No, it's fine.

\n< Serena >Indeed, there is fear. There were also aspects
that I underestimated.

\n< Serena >However, there is something I must do from now on.
So, I will move forward. There is no choice but to
continue.
\n<Guild Master>Tch.

\n<Guild Master>Well... for now, since the goblins are gone, the
request is considered complete.

\n<Guild Master>Here, your reward. Go to sleep, eat, and take a
bath quickly.
\n< Serena >....
\n< Serena >...This makes it x0 more to go.
'　危うい所だったが、なんとか依頼は完了した。'
'　今日はもう帰って休もう…。'
'ゴブリンに負けた'
